Package acsse.csc3a.map

Class AbstractMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
acsse.csc3a.map.AbstractMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - A key that must be a point
V -
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<K,V>, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdjacencyMap
public abstract class AbstractMap<K,V> extends Object implements Map<K,V>
Specialized abstract Hash Map, specialized to b tailor point hashing (where the index of the point is used in the hashing)
